title: Give Me Strength by Kate McCarthy (Give Me, #2).epub
description:
Quinn Salisbury is struggling to leave behind her violent past. Accepting a position as assistant manager to rock band, Jamieson, she meets Travis Valentine, the older brother of her boss. Their attraction is intense, but when her past resurfaces, she pushes him away until a staggering secret is revealed that leaves her running for her life. Can Quinn find the strength to fight for her future? 

Genre: Romance
